# Archived Configurations

This folder contains deprecated configuration files.

## Archive Policy
- Configurations replaced by newer versions
- Parameters that were optimized away
- Legacy settings no longer used

## Archive Contents
- Original config file
- Date archived
- Reason for archiving

## Format
Each archived config should be saved as:
`archived/configs/[config_name]_v[X.X.X]_archived_[YYYY-MM-DD].yaml`

